<TITLE>
Ayas (Ayash, Ayashe, Ayaas, Iyash), a Cree-Ojibway hero
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Ayas (or Ayash), 
epic hero of the Cree and Anishinabe tribes.">
